    public abstract class ArchiveFileSystem
extends NewVirtualFileSystem

      • extractLocalPath

        protected abstract java.lang.String extractLocalPath(java.lang.String rootPath)
        Strips any separator chars from a root (obtained via VfsUtilCore.getRootFile(com.intellij.openapi.vfs.VirtualFile) path to obtain a path to a local file.

      • composeRootPath

        protected abstract java.lang.String composeRootPath(java.lang.String localPath)
        A reverse to extractLocalPath(String) - i.e. dresses a local file path to make it a suitable root path for this filesystem. E.g. "/x/y.jar" -> "/x/y.jar!/"
